Distribution: The subspecies inhabits a contiguous wide area along the Adriatic coast, approximately from Otočac in Lika (
Croatia
) in NW to SE of Trebinje (
Bosnia
and 
Hercegovina
) in SE. It seems to be absent from the central Velebit mountains (
Croatia
), but it is present in the detached peninsula Pelješac and the islands of Brač and Ugljan. The populations W and NW of Otočac were not available for study (

Figure 
1

).
